item.title: [HIVE-19687] Export table on acid partitioned table is failing
item.description:
Reproducer

create table exportPartitionTable(id int, name string) partitioned by(country string) clustered by (id) into 2 buckets  stored as orc tblproperties ("transactional"="true");
export table exportPartitionTable PARTITION (country='india') to '/tmp/exportDataStore';

Error

FAILED: SemanticException [Error 10004]: Line 1:165 Invalid table alias or column reference 'india': (possible column names are: id, name, country)
item.summary: Export table on acid partitioned table is failing

status.description: The issue is considered finished, the resolution is correct. Issues which are not closed can be reopened.

comments.comment: ekoifman Can you take a look?
what if partition column is an INTEGER? what will this do?
Hmm quotes should be done only for string types.
